  "description": "Safe arithmetic library for C++20 and above. Safe arithmetic ensures correctness of arithmetic operations at compile-time. It protects against overflow, underflow, divide by zero, and out-of-bounds index access. This provides both functional correctness as well as greater protection against related security threats.",
  "description_ja": "C++20以降向けの安全な算術演算ライブラリ。コンパイル時に算術演算の正確性を保証し、オーバーフロー・アンダーフロー・ゼロ除算・範囲外インデックスアクセスを防止することで、機能的正確性とセキュリティ上の脅威への保護を提供する",
